85506cd717a54999c","tid":2012512,"uid":195260,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"cadc72cc0f47f90e58d4db74ac427bc52dd7c1f8","tid":2012512,"uid":213914,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a703ade5e4bd0d319e760d27516639ab7e849fee","tid":2012512,"uid":303419,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T18:03:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得睇能力+喜好<br />\n<br />\n想月球 眼科 皮膚科<br />\n想研究 病理 Microbio <br />\n手巧、有能力 外科 <br />\n穩定 GP Family Med"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T18:10:45.000Z","msg":"我對surgery幾有興趣，不過聽人講個work life balance 好差，而且個專科試pass rate好似都勁低。巴打你係醫生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"做ward嘅就其實係忙㗎嘞 只係surgery嘅每日嘅工時長少少啫<br />\n出得黎醫院行 esp ward 見病人嗰啲 好多時都預咗要 call / shift<br />\n<br />\n專科試就聽講最低唔係surgery (而surgery都好少聽話係&quot;特別&quot;難)<br />\n其實考得specialty都預咗係難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係med school 保pass (at least at the end)<br />\n<br />\n我諗可以到clinical years 先feel吓個specialty 嘅 approach同life係咪啱你<br />\n始終有咁多科可以揀 (如果有得揀)<br />\n<br />\n利申: 非醫生"},{"pid":"c67e9b13df2435a0f37f0723d2ded2e7afa96566","tid":2012512,"uid":1025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cadc72cc0f47f90e58d4db74ac427bc52dd7c1f8","tid":2012512,"uid":213914,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a703ade5e4bd0d319e760d27516639ab7e849fee","tid":2012512,"uid":303419,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T18:03:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得睇能力+喜好<br />\n<br />\n想月球 眼科 皮膚科<br />\n想研究 病理 Microbio <br />\n手巧、有能力 外科 <br />\n穩定 GP Family Med"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T18:10:45.000Z","msg":"我對surgery幾有興趣，不過聽人講個work life balance 好差，而且個專科試pass rate好似都勁低。巴打你係醫生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"你有無決心係ha 做十年先 你入養和都要你做夠5年專科先有admission right"},{"pid":"80c996d1f4766b7fa4bc8ef6de46c0b5dd100af1","tid":2012512,"uid":195260,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"679b476e2a482439b69faa1123b82590947ca6a0","tid":2012512,"uid":213914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"有冇醫生巴打可以分享下揀專科嘅過程？我宜家yr2，想知之後揀專科主要係睇成績定係睇其他野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:12:01.000Z","msg":"講就叫揀專科，實際上係「R training post」<br />\n所以就視乎你houseman 嗰時嘅表現好唔好，你有無同定啲department打好關係等等，令到佢肯offer呢個training post畀你<br />\n(講到好似真係要打好關係咁，其實係要houseman揀佢個department做，咁佢都知你係個點嘅人，或者係有好嘅工作表現，同埋有啲department 只係請做過嘅ho)<br />\n同埋好重要：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">究竟佢有無呢個training post開畀你</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n講到最後就係求職見工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9d63a1c98031365f556f6b48c6840fb4b4dd25","tid":2012512,"uid":52972,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"冷門少少， 其實麻醉幾好撈。 相當hea 少少， 而且做到好大年紀都仲做得。 你揸刀60都手震啦。"},{"pid":"f69f742db3c24132a6952be108ecc9c19e5c9200","tid":2012512,"uid":151387,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7e9d63a1c98031365f556f6b48c6840fb4b4dd25","tid":2012512,"uid":52972,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"冷門少少， 其實麻醉幾好撈。 相當hea 少少， 而且做到好大年紀都仲做得。 你揸刀60都手震啦。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"麻醉手震點插喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c73220df657c411c02315ded7a36867229efca","tid":2012512,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f69f742db3c24132a6952be108ecc9c19e5c9200","tid":2012512,"uid":151387,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7e9d63a1c98031365f556f6b48c6840fb4b4dd25","tid":2012512,"uid":52972,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"冷門少少， 其實麻醉幾好撈。 相當hea 少少， 而且做到好大年紀都仲做得。 你揸刀60都手震啦。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"麻醉手震點插喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"大家都手震 ，你情願俾佢插喉定俾佢割包皮。"},{"pid":"530c64bbd774b7de022d9749e